Secretary ops: `02-areas/secretary/secretary-overview.md` — ICP, voice, rate limits, suppression; queue `00-inbox/secretary-queue/`; log `03-resources/secretary-log/`.

Re-index after vault edits: `mempalace mine /Users/mushood/Documents/code/coeus`

