## PARA layout

- `00-inbox/` — captures; **`secretary-queue/`** — today's outreach candidates
- `01-projects/` — live deployments
- `02-areas/` — career, **startups**, **secretary** (ICP, voice, caps, suppression), immigration
- `03-resources/` — github-repos, resumes, social-profiles, infrastructure, **secretary-log**
- `04-archives/` — inactive

## Sensitive (gitignored, local only)

finance/, career/companies/, career/education/, musings/, personal-notes/, travel/, colab-notebooks/, ai-experiments/ — use MemPalace search if indexed; do not expose externally.
